:{{DIcon|Talk}} What exactly is the Ambrosial Arbor made of?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000134: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act90000134.json-->
::'''Howard:''' I'm also curious about that... Wait! Stop right there!
::'''Howard:''' It is a top secret on the Xianzhou. Didn't you see how things were when that giant tree grew? It was heavily guarded by people from the Realm-Keeping Commission and the Cloud Knights were on patrol.
::'''Howard:''' I heard that the Ambrosial Arbor is an Aeonspawn. I'm not sure whether it is true, but seeing how seriously Xianzhou treats the issue, I suggest that you stay away from the tree and don't dabble in their taboo.
::'''Howard:''' Before every business trip, my colleagues always remind me to respect the local customs, or be ready to bear the consequences. You should be careful with your actions when travelling, too!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
